metadata.name: Hometown Series - Clouds in Hometown
metadata.description:
This NFT is a digital work based on the artist's original artwork and includes the artist's signature. A total of ten copies will be issued.

The purpose of issuing NFTs of original artwork is to promote the artist's work and will also enable artists, especially emerging artists, to generate income through NFT artwork to focus on their artwork.

This format will replace artwork donations and benefit artists more directly.

To view and purchase original artwork, please click on the links below.

https://www.riwatech.com/zh/products/%E6%9E%97%E6%9F%84%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%B0%B4%E5%A2%A8-%E6%95%85%E4%B9%A1%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-%E6%95%85%E4%B9%A1%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%91
